      <conclusions>
         <blockContainer class="explanatoryNotes">
            <heading>EXPLANATORY NOTE</heading>
            <block name="comment">(This note is not part of the Regulations)</block>
            <p>These Regulations amend the Local Government Pension Scheme (Miscellaneous Amendments) (Scotland) Regulations 2019 to amend two minor errors. These Regulations amend regulation 2 of those Regulations and come into force on the same date as regulation 2 and have effect from the date that regulation 2 has effect.</p>
